config ACK_ENABLED_MULTI_TID
	bool
	default y
	help
	 This enables CLI command interface only.
	 You need to configure it using CLI command.
	 'mac tweak tx <vif (0 | 1)> <option> <num> <len: optional>' 
	 option: Configure tweak
	   Set 0 to disable tweak
	   Set 1 to enable quick-BA session agreements
	   Set 2 to build wait single-tid a-mpdu(s)
	   Set 3 to build single-tid a-mpdu(s) with test qos frame(s)
	   Set 4 to build multi-tid a-mpdu(s) with test qos frame(s)
	   Set 5 to build ack-enabled multi-tid a-mpdu(s) with test mgmt/qos frame(s)
	   Set 6 to build wait multi-tid a-mpdu(s)
	 num: Number of wait MPDU to be TX (in option 2) or
	      Number of test QoS frame(s) to be injected (in other options, skippable)
	 len(optional): Length of test QoS frame(s) to be injected
	      In case of mode 6, len is replaced to TID

